            <title>[LU-4202] Test failure sanity-lfsck test_8: Expect &apos;scanning-phase2&apos;, but got &apos;scanning-phase1&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4202</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b6717d88-4462-11e3-8472-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b6717d88-4462-11e3-8472-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_8 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(22) Expect &apos;scanning-phase2&apos;, but got &apos;scanning-phase1&apos;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-lfsck 8&lt;/p&gt;</description>
