                            <comment id="70820" author="bzzz" created="Wed, 6 Nov 2013 06:25:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I changed number of objects in test 8 to 20K and run the test again:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;average_speed_phase1: 5254 items/sec&lt;br/&gt;
average_speed_phase2: N/A&lt;br/&gt;
